                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 9.15,
                                "byte_start": 100530,
                                "byte_stop": 137206,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion in 76-422, Dothard against Rawlinson will also be announced by Mr. Justice Stewart."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.15,
                        "stop": 242.558,
                        "byte_start": 137206,
                        "byte_stop": 1070822,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15043,
                            "name": "Potter Stewart",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/potter_stewart",
                            "last_name": "Stewart",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2687,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": -353962800,
                                    "date_end": 362984400,
                                    "appointing_president": "Dwight D. Eisenhower",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2687"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32752,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 56350,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/potter_stewart.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 8298,
                            "identifier": "potter_stewart"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 9.15,
                                "stop": 18.138,
                                "byte_start": 137206,
                                "byte_stop": 173150,
                                "text": "This case comes to us on direct appeal from a three-judge Federal District Court for the Middle District of Alabama."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 18.138,
                                "stop": 32.217,
                                "byte_start": 173150,
                                "byte_stop": 229470,
                                "text": "The appellee, Dianne Rawlinson sought employment as a prison guard with the Alabama Board of Corrections and her application for employment and that job was rejected."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 32.217,
                                "stop": 44.823,
                                "byte_start": 229470,
                                "byte_stop": 279834,
                                "text": "She then brought this class suit alleging that she had been denied employment because of her sex in violation of Title VII of the Civil Rights Act of 1964 as amended."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 44.823,
                                "stop": 53.587,
                                "byte_start": 279834,
                                "byte_stop": 314943,
                                "text": "The Board of Corrections follows two employment policies that the District Court concluded do violate Title VII."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 53.587,
                                "stop": 64.14,
                                "byte_start": 314943,
                                "byte_stop": 357157,
                                "text": "By statute, Alabama requires that every prison guard must be at least 5\u20192\u201d tall and weigh at least 120 pounds."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 64.14,
                                "stop": 80.113,
                                "byte_start": 357157,
                                "byte_stop": 421000,
                                "text": "The District Court found that the statutory criteria disproportionately exclude women from employment and that the State had failed to offer any evidence that the height and weight standards are job-related."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 80.113,
                                "stop": 99.774,
                                "byte_start": 421000,
                                "byte_stop": 499681,
                                "text": "Secondly, by an official regulation, the State has established a policy of not hiring any women as guards in so-called contact positions in all male maximum security penitentiaries, whatever the height or weight of the women guards might be."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 99.774,
                                "stop": 113.551,
                                "byte_start": 499681,
                                "byte_stop": 554747,
                                "text": "The District Court held that these regulations explicit discrimination on the basis of sex was not justified under the bona-fide-occupational-qualification exception contained in Title VII."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 113.551,
                                "stop": 125.991,
                                "byte_start": 554747,
                                "byte_stop": 604589,
                                "text": "In an opinion filed with the clerk today, we affirmed the District Court\u0027s invalidation of the height and weight requirements but reversed its invalidation of the official regulation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 125.991,
                                "stop": 144.301,
                                "byte_start": 604589,
                                "byte_stop": 677836,
                                "text": "The District Court properly relied on national height and weight statistics showing that 41% of the female population and less than 1% of the male population would be excluded from any prison guard employment under Alabama statutory height and weight standards."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 144.301,
                                "stop": 156.925,
                                "byte_start": 677836,
                                "byte_stop": 728305,
                                "text": "The State failed to rebut this prima facie case by demonstrating either deficiencies in the statistical data or that the height and weight standards are job-related."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 156.925,
                                "stop": 172.039,
                                "byte_start": 728305,
                                "byte_stop": 788700,
                                "text": "Secondly, we agree with the District Court that Titles VII bona-fide-occupational-qualification exception is an extremely narrow exception to the acts general prohibition of discrimination on the basis of sex."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 172.039,
                                "stop": 183.267,
                                "byte_start": 788700,
                                "byte_stop": 833630,
                                "text": "On the facts of this case, however, we conclude that the explicit gender discrimination and the official regulation is within the statutory exception."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 183.267,
                                "stop": 200.265,
                                "byte_start": 833630,
                                "byte_stop": 901653,
                                "text": "Alabama\u0027s all male maximum security prisons are so violent and disorganized that sexual attacks on women guards are likely both to occur and to exacerbate the problem of maintaining institutional security."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 200.265,
                                "stop": 216.9,
                                "byte_start": 901653,
                                "byte_stop": 968213,
                                "text": "In these circumstances, we conclude that being male is a bona -- is a bona-fide-occupational-qualification for the job of guard in a contact position in Alabama\u0027s all male maximum security penitentiaries."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 216.9,
                                "stop": 231.459,
                                "byte_start": 968213,
                                "byte_stop": 1026414,
                                "text": "I am authorized to say that Mr. Justice Rehnquist has filed an opinion joining only part of the Court\u0027s opinion and concurring in the judgment, an opinion in which the Chief Justice and Mr. Justice Blackmun have joined."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 231.459,
                                "stop": 242.558,
                                "byte_start": 1026414,
                                "byte_stop": 1070822,
                                "text": "Mr. Justice Marshall joined by Mr. Justice Brennan has filed an opinion dissenting in part and Mr. Justice White has also filed a dissenting opinion."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
